r />\n或者我既夢係好小 或者直接幫唔到咩忙<br />\n但我敢對自己講 我無成為自己細個討厭既人"},{"pid":"2217b8fc63f2d6072be91673371fb4b32f38cea9","tid":1251703,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T19:42:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53c6a7c6796cecb1938907a45deb8ee991ed9a4e","tid":1251703,"uid":84409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T19:42:20.000Z","msg":"唔使心淡，未來仲有漫漫長路去成長<br />\n再講，連續咁多日咁繃緊既氣氛對精神健康都唔好，去玩下放鬆下，需要時歸隊就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7514454b5df4a9fbc9a852d93042eff4648cf9","tid":1251703,"uid":80107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T19:43:48.000Z","msg":"其實大家都好明白香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以話 200萬真係一個奇跡嚟<br />\n好可能係最後一次靠呢個方式吸引到外國傳媒關注<br />\n好可能係我地最後機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cfcef73c3e78897af773e46a769b714ce72321e","tid":1251703,"uid":31623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T19:48:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ebf4642856bdb13c2e141eb95caef4894c26669","tid":1251703,"uid":31623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T19:50:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}